{% from "components/accordion-list/macro.njk" import accordionList %}
{% from "components/accordion-list-item/macro.njk" import accordionListItem %}

<h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>
{% call accordionList() %}
  {% call accordionListItem({ summary: "How do I book an appointment?" }) %}
    <p>Use the online booking system or call reception.</p>
  {% endcall %}
  {% call accordionListItem({ summary: "How do I cancel an appointment?" }) %}
    <p>Give at least 24 hours' notice so the slot can be offered to someone else.</p>
  {% endcall %}
  {% call accordionListItem({ summary: "What should I bring?" }) %}
    <p>Bring ID, your current medication list, and any relevant test results.</p>
  {% endcall %}
{% endcall %}

<h2>Accessibility</h2>
<p>An <code>&lt;ol&gt;</code> expresses the hierarchical order of
  the sections. Each section is a separate <code>&lt;li&gt;</code>
  with its own disclosure.</p>
